sourceMeaningMnemonic: Your <radical>shellfish</radical> are worth a <radical>fortune</radical> because you decided to <kanji>paste</kanji> your fortune to the shellfish.
meaningInfo: Picture all of your riches, your money, your jewels. They're all pasted directly onto all of your shellfish!
readingMnemonic: You're a little crazy, which is why you decided to use <kanji>paste</kanji> to paste your entire fortune to these shellfish, and as you paste each one you yell out, "<reading>Ha</reading> (<ja>は</ja>)!" Paste.
readingInfo: "Ha ha!" Paste paste. "Ha ha ha!!" PASTE PASTE PASTE.
